N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 24.8 - Unacceptable practice protocols

State Regulations

The Committee on the Professions shall review and determine
appeals from findings of unacceptable practice protocols involving nurse
practitioners and collaborating physicians. Notes
